**###Before Save###****###Before Save###****###Before Activate###**bktype = NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2") bktypelist = Array("CHAPTER 11","CHAPTER 13")
'Field colors ' NLSapp.SetFieldAttribute "TASK_DETAIL_UDF16", RGB(0,0,0), RGB(255,248,220), true
'Hide fields 'Proof of Claim If isdate(NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF12")) = True Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF19", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF20", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF21", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF30", False End if
'BK type is 11 or 13 for each x in bktypelist if x = bktype Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF13", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF14", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF15", False End if next
'Enable fields 'List of Creditors If Not NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF17") = "YES" Then NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF18", false End if
NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", False
If Not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Bankruptcy type must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If Not IsDate(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF3")) = False Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("Date filed must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF6")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Court must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF22")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Case # must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again." NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", True End If End If End If End If
**###Before Activate###****###Before Create###****###Before Create###****###On Delete###****###On Delete###****###After Save###**bktype = NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2") bktypelist = Array("CHAPTER 11","CHAPTER 13") taskstatus = NLSApp.getField("TASK_STATUS") taskrefno = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_NLS_REFNO")
'Field colors 'N/A
'Hide fields 'Proof of Claim If isdate(NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF12")) = True Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF19", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF20", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF21", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF30", False End if
'BK type is 11 or 13 for each x in bktypelist if x = bktype Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF13", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF14", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF15", False End if next
'Enable fields 'List of Creditors If Not NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF17") = "YES" Then NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF18", false End if
NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", False
If Not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Bankruptcy type must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If Not IsDate(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF3")) = False Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("Date filed must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF6")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Court must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF22")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Case # must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again." NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", True End If End If End If End If
If NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF24") = "CHECK" and Not taskstatus = "BK-ACTIVE" and Not taskstatus = "BK-INVALID" and Not taskstatus = "BK-DISMISSED" then 'NLSapp.SaveScreen() NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement("SELECT 0; UPDATE task SET status_code_id = " & TEMPLATE_STATUS_BK_FILED & " WHERE task_refno = " & NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_REFNO")) NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus taskrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE,"ADD" 'NLSapp.RefreshScreen()
Else If Not taskstatus = "BK-NOTICE" then If taskstatus = "BK-INVALID" or taskstatus = "BK-DISMISSED" then 'NLSapp.SaveScreen() NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus taskrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_NOTICE,"DELETE" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus taskrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE,"DELETE" 'LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE 'NLSapp.RefreshScreen() Else 'NLSapp.SaveScreen() NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement("SELECT 0; UPDATE task SET status_code_id = " & TEMPLATE_STATUS_BK_NOTICE & " WHERE task_refno = " & NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_REFNO")) NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus taskrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE,"DELETE" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus taskrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_NOTICE,"ADD" 'NLSapp.RefreshScreen() End if End if End if**###After Save###****###After Create###****###After Create###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###Local Functions###** Sub PacerVerification (bktype,filedt,courtval,caseno,pacercheckyn,taskrefno) 'Evaluates 4 fields and if any are not filled it will not enable a field (usredef24) for editing If Not len(bktype) = 0 Then 'A Bankruptcy type must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked If Not IsDate(filedt) = False Then 'Date filed must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked If not len(courtval) = 0 Then 'A Court must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked. If not len(caseno) = 0 Then 'A Case # must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked. NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", True End If End If End If End If
End sub**###Local Functions###**
